432589 THE KHADI AND VILLAGE INDUSTRIES COMMISSION (AMENDMENT) ACT, 2006
NO. 10 OF 2006 [ 22nd March, 2006.]
An Act further to amend the Khadi and Village Industries Commission Act, 1956.
BE it enacted by Parliament in the Fifty- seventh Year of the Republic of India as follows:-
623144 1 Short title and commencement.-
1452497 1This Act may be called the Khadi and Village Industries Commission (Amendment) Act, 2006.
1195492 2It shall come into force on such date as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in this behalf.
1025053 2 Amendment of section 2.- In section 2 of the Khadi and Village Industries Commission Act, 1956 (61 of 1956) (hereinafter referred to as the principal Act),-
176832 iin clause (ff), for the words" ten thousand", the words" twenty thousand" shall be substituted;
249410 iiin clause (h), in sub- clause (i),-
16647 Afor the words" fifteen thousand rupees", the words" one lakh rupees" shall be substituted;
441854 Bafter the proviso, the following proviso shall be inserted, namely:- ' Provided further that in the case of any industry located in a hilly area, the provisions of this sub- clause shall have effect as if for the words" one lakh rupees", the words" one lakh and fifty thousand rupees" had been substituted.'. 3.
Amendment of section 4.
442251 3 Amendment of section 4.- In section 4 of the principal Act,-
1284841 aafter sub- section (1), the following sub- section shall be inserted, namely:- " (1A) Save as otherwise provided under this Act and the rules made thereunder, the exercise of all powers and discharge of all functions under this Act, including general superintendence, direction and management of day- to- day affairs of the Commission, shall vest in the Commission.";
650778 bin sub- section (2),-
311794 iin clause (a), for the words" having specialised knowledge and experience of khadi and village industries", the words" having specialised knowledge and not less than ten years of experience of khadi or village industries" shall be substituted;
1000576 iifor clause (b), the following clause shall be substituted, namely:-
